text: Abid Ali is a Bangladesh Awami League politician and the former Member of Parliament of Rangpur-5. ==Career== Ali was elected to parliament from Rangpur-5 as a Bangladesh Awami League candidate in 1973. ==References== Category:Awami League politicians Category:Living people Category:1st Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Abid Ali (politician)
